metadata.name: Tetro Land - I
metadata.description:
After many years, human beings were finally able to discover another world in which there was life like our own world, a great and beautiful world full of blessings, all beings in it were cheerful and happy.
 The nutrition of these creatures was fungi that were found in abundance throughout this vast land and it can be said that this food has played an important role in the evolution of such creatures in this land.
 In this world, you can hear the colors and taste the sounds...
Welcome to Tetro Land
